name: AMEFormat

properties.name: extension
properties.description: The file name extension used by this format.

methods.name: requestPresets
methods.description: Request the available user match source and system presets for this format from Adobe Media Encoder. An event with type AMEPresetsEvent.EVENT_RequestPresetsSuccess or AMEPresetsEvent.EVENT_RequestPresetsError will be sent to notify about success or failure.
methods.longdesc: Request the available presets for this format from AME.

description: AMEFormat represents a format of the Adobe Media Encoder
